<p class="courseblockdesc">
Survey of industrial and graphic design from the Industrial Revolution to 1925. Course Information: Same as <a href="/search/?P=AH%20235" title="AH&#160;235" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'AH 235');">AH&#160;235</a>. Prerequisite(s): 3 hours of Art History at the 100-level or consent of the instructor.<br />
</p>
</div><div class="courseblock">
