<p class="courseblockdesc">
Survey of industrial and graphic design from 1925 to the present. Course Information: Same as <a href="/search/?P=AH%20236" title="AH&#160;236" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'AH 236');">AH&#160;236</a>. Prerequisite(s): 3 hours of Art History at the 100-level or consent of the instructor. Recommended background: <a href="/search/?P=AH%20235" title="AH&#160;235" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'AH 235');">AH&#160;235</a> or <a href="/search/?P=DES%20235" title="DES&#160;235" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'DES 235');">DES&#160;235</a>.<br />
