<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>DES&#160;240.  Visualization I.  4 hours.</strong></p>
<p class="courseblockdesc">
Freehand sketch intensive studio with focus on rapid conceptional visualization.  Course Information: Previously listed as AD 223. Extensive computer use required. Prerequisite(s): Sophomore standing or above. Class Schedule Information: To be properly registered, students must enroll in one Lecture and one Laboratory.<br />
